# YouTube Homepage Clone

A pixel-perfect clone of YouTube's homepage built with 
pure HTML and CSS — no frameworks.

## Features
- Responsive header with search bar and icons
- Left sidebar navigation
- Video card grid layout
- Built using Flexbox and CSS Grid

## Tools Used
HTML, CSS, Flexbox, CSS Grid

## What I Learned
- CSS Flexbox for header and sidebar layouts
- CSS Grid for video card arrangement
- Organizing CSS across multiple stylesheets
- Positioning elements with CSS

